Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.20,0:00:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.87,0:00:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，房間光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並保持好適當距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.58,0:00:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了!主人的房子會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.89,0:00:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手唷!主人的房子會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被摧毀的...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.71,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小沙希，停手唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要破壞妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手唷，停手唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼...久留美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼妳不戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她應該是很強橫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要破壞妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別去!仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事嗎?久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.03,0:03:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，請離開這裡唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳為甚麼不戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像受軍隊襲擊時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要服從主人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，你剛才說不可以用暴力唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.12,0:04:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手!不可用暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳不戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎會這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裡，主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以用...暴力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要破壞妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希...小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼回事...突然間...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.36,0:06:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她死了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是怎樣啟動她的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以軍隊的科技是沒可能做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用電擊活性化令她「休性起動」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是令她完全甦醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希小姐是在睡眠狀態下戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.68,0:06:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「休性起動」?是妳想出來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是布蘭度博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.79,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沙希的起動實驗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說來協助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭度!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也來了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要趕快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她是繼久留美之後的二號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本想強化她的神經回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在變成可以勉強啟動...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號機?   就像是妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小沙希是久留美的妹妹嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我多了一個妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要慶祝一下唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對小沙希而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要為多了一個姐姐而慶祝唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，起...身...唷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小沙希，起身唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.91,0:07:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，和久留美那時一樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和久留美一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像當時對久留美所做的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對小沙希也做一次唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再做...一次...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?還是叫我「小姐」唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...我不可以直呼妳的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為...久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是久...留...美...唷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳雖然這樣說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...這樣下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次啟動沙希的可能，性...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，我忍耐你叫我小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你對小沙希再做一次...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時對我做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就...請...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...想幹甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一方法是接吻呢!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種方法怎可能啟動她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也以為是不可能的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請快點唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.79,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人始終只是屬於久留美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以屬於其他人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...怎辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美去幹唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然久留美的咀唇也只屬於主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在沒法子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小沙希...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小沙希，好極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒來了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎會!?沒可能的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個ANGEL HEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,產生共鳴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好唷，小沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美是小沙希的姐姐唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心在卜卜跳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教，小沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我檢查妳的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是屬於妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過份了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐，妳沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像受到重創呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你擔心我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.18,0:10:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很開心唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好辛苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.13,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔...是我說對不起才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在適當的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使出妳的力量也沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在適當...的時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.20,0:11:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美...不明白唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，主人教我便行唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你以後甚麼事情也教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好...好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟...甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士，你振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.91,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我出手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像重了點呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這把聲音是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然破壞久留美的計劃失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.59,0:12:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在帶你回去，綾小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾小路博士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我多了一個妹妹唷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集開始的新發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐愛的生活開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?那麼綾小路博士的事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使久留美，第六話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「愛姊妹」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集開始有新發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐二人的愛的生活開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二人在浴場一起沐浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引人入勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希，妳的，性格改變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這才是真正的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛的鋼鐵天使，沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使久留美，第六話
